display_long_description:
A portal to the Universe! Experience genuine love, money, & career readings in a fresh, fully-immersive virtual environment. Tarot card readings with Tarot expert ‘Aura’ have come to life for the first time in VR.

🔮FEEL TRULY CONNECTED
Tarot Life enables its users to feel like they are genuinely closer to the Tarot reader. Owing to the realistic visuals; calm & soothing environment, users get a platform where they can interact with Virtual Tarot Reader with Aura and get divine guidance. 

🔮READINGS YOU REALLY NEED:
Get unheard but accurate conclusions about your past, present, & future. Here, you can ask any concern & Aura will help you address them with:
✔️Love Tarot Readings
✔️Money Tarot Readings
✔️Career Tarot Readings

🔮CLASSIC TAROT READING EXPERIENCE, NOW IN VR:
Brought to life with a beautiful, hand-painted, Rider Waite inspired  tarot deck, a collaboration of the 🎴 22 Major Arcana cards & the energy surrounding you will provide you the medium to look into your future.
